drm/i915/skl: Swapping 90 and 270 to be compliant with Xrandr

Since DRM_ROTATE is counter clockwise (which is compliant with Xrandr),
and HW rotation is clockwise, swapping 90/270 to work as expected from
userspace.

v2: Rebased

